  <brief_title>Safety Study of the Novel Drug Dimebon to Treat Patients With Huntington's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Phase 1-2A, Open-Label, Dosage-Escalation and Randomized, Double-Blinded, Placebo-Controlled Study of Dimebon in Subjects With Huntington's Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
